                     <interp inst="t18260216-67-person586" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming down Broad-street, and felt some person run against me; I turned round, and saw the prisoner close to me, and the lard rolling on the ground - he crossed the street, ran against a woman, and then walked on; I pursued, and took him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I am a poor man.</p>
